Pathing is worse than ever (please try pul stuff in PoS).<br>
Tons of diffrent Flag issues, there is something wrong then a single person can ruin a raid. I seen people blew maze in PoN by just hailing. I seen a idiotic bard charm a Desert giant in PoS just to blew the Lord cycle (was petitioned, hopefully he get banned since it was on purpose). The list could go on.<br>
<br>
The core issue, Verant have no clue how we play the game. And next expansion I acctually hope they have people to test it first, people that acctaully like to point out the flaws instead.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=krilenspiritlink>Krilen Spiritlink</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 560<br> <font color=#333333>(12/1/02 5:42:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8011.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: dumb.....</span><hr size=1> I completely disagree, Zeem. I thought this expansion for the most part showed that the designers know how players play the game, and can make challenging content that those players will like.<br>
